# Risk Assessment Engine

## Purpose

Transform technical findings into measurable organizational risk using vulnerability severity, asset criticality, exploitability, and compliance impact.

---

## Inputs

- Correlated Vulnerability Findings
- CVSS Scores
- Asset Criticality
- Threat Intelligence
- Compliance Results
- Manual Risk Exceptions

---

## Processing

- Remove duplicate vulnerabilities.
- Calculate likelihood.
- Calculate business impact.
- Generate organizational risk score.
- Prioritize remediation.
- Produce heat map data.

---

## Outputs

- Risk Register
- Executive Heat Map
- Prioritized Findings
- Risk Trends
- Remediation Queue

---

## Metrics

|Metric|Description|
|---|---|
|Organizational Risk Score|Overall enterprise risk|
|Critical Findings|Active critical vulnerabilities|
|Average CVSS|Mean severity score|
|Risk Trend|Monthly change|
|High Risk Assets|Assets above defined threshold|

